,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"各位，飲料都拿好了嗎～？\n那麼月森聖誕派對就要開始囉！　乾杯～～～！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"event242-03-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"喔～，真是壯觀啊。\n那麼寬敞的宴會廳居然擠進了這麼多人耶","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event242-03-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"最後，是幾乎所有月森生\n都參加了嗎？　好厲害……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"event242-03-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"真不愧是透透。果然是交友廣泛啊～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event242-03-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"那麼，我就去聽演奏會了。\n等等見","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event242-03-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"呵呵，看來他真的很期待\n交響樂團的演奏會呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event242-03-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"瑠唯同學，是不是很難得地心浮氣躁啊？\n我看他好像一直在確認時間","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"event242-03-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"有喔有喔！　「派對能不能趕快開始呢～」\n像這樣很明顯地寫在臉上了喔～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event242-03-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"那我們也移動吧。\n難得的自助式派對，要吃很～多菜喔？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event242-03-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"唔，嗯","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"event242-03-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"？　你該不會是在緊張……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event242-03-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"有一點點……雖然我學了很多禮儀\n但還是會很擔心如果失敗了怎麼辦而戰戰兢兢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"event242-03-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"沒問～題。白白的話一定能做得很完美啦。\n你的背，也有挺得直直的喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event242-0